Sun Sep 29 16:44:46 GMT 2013  Olly Betts <olly@survex.com>

	* Backport change from trunk:
	* backends/brass/,backends/chert/,backends/flint,backends/dbcheck.cc:
	  Fix database consistency checking to always open all the tables at
	  the same revision, which could lead to false errors being reported
	  after a commit interrupted by the process being killed or the
	  machine crashing.  Reported by Joey Hess in
	  http://bugs.debian.org/724610

