Tue Jan 08 09:05:56 GMT 2013  Olly Betts <olly@survex.com>

	* backends/brass/brass_database.cc,backends/chert/chert_database.cc,
	  backends/flint/flint_database.cc,net/remoteconnection.cc,
	  tests/api_replicate.cc: Pass O_BINARY when opening replication
	  related files in some places where we weren't before, which will
	  probably help solve bugs such as #472.  Changes are roughly
	  equivalent in effect to r16961 and r16962 on trunk, but done in a
	  very different way to be less invasive.

