	* Backport changes from trunk:
	* Makefile.am,languages/Makefile.mk,queryparser/Makefile.mk,
	  tests/Makefile.am: In automake, INCLUDES is now deprecated in favour
	  of AM_CPPFLAGS so update to use the latter.
	* bin/Makefile.mk: INCLUDES is always used, AM_CPPFLAGS
	  isn't if there are per-executable CPPFLAGS, so add AM_CPPFLAGS
	  explicitly when we use per-executable CPPFLAGS.

