	* matcher/rset.cc: Improve debugging messages.

Wed Nov 21 14:26:44 GMT 2007  Richard Boulton <richard@lemurconsulting.com>

	* matcher/remotesubmatch.cc: Add some debugging, and reorder the
	  header includes.

